{"tid":1470178,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"七百港鐵車長要求港鐵譴責警方影響鐵路安全","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:58:53.000Z","uid":20933,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3b715b9c8b606d5dff55abc3bce87c114821c979","tid":1470178,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"港鐵超過約700名車長及列車員工督察聯署，要求港鐵譴責警方各種影響鐵路安全的行動，不要盲目配合警方要求。數名車長戴上口罩及頭盔，到九龍灣港鐵總部大樓遞交聯署聲明，指如港鐵未能回應訴求，車長會考慮以保障人身安全為理由，請假或拒絕開車。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，港鐵面對警方7月21日緩慢處理元朗站暴力事件、在葵芳站內施放催淚彈，以及在太古站扶手電梯上向撤離中的乘客開槍等，只表示「非常遺憾」而沒有譴責，欠缺阻嚇力，增加前線工作壓力，亦令工作環境倍添危險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聲明又指，警方施放催淚彈後，有毒粒子會依附在車站、列車及通風系統，要求公司在徹底清除有毒粒子前，要向員工及乘客派發可過濾有機氣體的口罩。"},{"pid":"5c74952cee2bf1173392093fb5f8cad55dedb35a","tid":1470178,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:25:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1152755&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1152755%26csid%3D261_341&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w6QBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=874106b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1152755&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"4ad380face6ee56c1dc2c0dfdf7247bca9da70ca","tid":1470178,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45cc61d0e1be6899dfde109dabb71a51ff5db7d","tid":1470178,"uid":119653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8aeebe3e06a01ee892f77d8a0daff9f99862877","tid":1470178,